FT  17 MAY 94 / UK Company News: Cape buys boards business for Pounds 3.2m
Cape has bought as a going concern the Pyrok Cementatious Building Boards
business from the receivers of Pyrok Group for Pounds 3.2m cash. Unaudited
management accounts for the nine months to December 31 indicate that Pyrok
Group sold boards with a value of Pounds 1.7m and incurred a pre-tax loss of
Pounds 200,000.
